text: Eva Karin Oscarsson-Göthberg (born 24 July 1953) is a Swedish equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Sweden Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
